The '''Alderaan Select Academy for Young Ladies''' was a school on [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]] for upper-class [[Gender/Legends|girls]], with Madame [[Vesta]] as the headmistress.<ref name="PLD">{{Tales|11|The Princess Leia Diaries}}</ref> All the daughters of [[Noble/Legends|nobility]], including [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]], attended. Students wore [[Color/Legends|white]] and blue uniforms. According to Leia, a number of the students exhibited "self-destructive" behavior.<ref name="CotJ">[[Children of the Jedi (novel)|''Children of the Jedi'']]</ref>

In [[0 BBY/Legends|0 BBY]] it was [[Destruction of Alderaan/Legends|destroyed]] along with Alderaan itself.<ref name="ANH" />

